text: Sharon Fichman and Jovana Jakšić were the defending champions, but decided not to participate this year. Francesca Di Lorenzo and Ronit Yurovsky won the title, defeating Marie-Alexandre Leduc and Charlotte Robillard-Millette 1–6, 7–5, [10–6] in the final. ==Seeds== ==Draw== ==References== *Main Draw Winnipeg National Bank Challenger Category:Winnipeg Challenger
